## 5. Architecture question

Building inside the existing Microsoft ecosystem (Power Apps / Power Automate) versus building outside it is a real fork — the first is gentler on patient-data regulatory exposure but constrains custom functionality; the second opens up capability but raises the compliance bar. This packet doesn't take a position. Worth thinking through together: which user stories actually need custom functionality, and which would Power Apps handle cleanly?

